78
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:43,490
[Thanks to everyone who created this world]
[With dreams as the horse, we will meet again]

79
00:07:43,490 --> 00:07:48,840
In this huge martial arts world, who do you think counts as a current hero?

80
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:52,580
Only those who have not experienced the pains of this world wish to become a hero.

81
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,340
Then how about those who have?

82
00:07:55,340 --> 00:08:03,360
[Path of Mountain and River]

83
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:15,870
♫ A lonely goose travels the world during sunset,
three autumns pass as if a moment ♫

84
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:22,500
♫ Listening to night rain on the parasol trees as
it wakes autumn and winter ♫

85
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:26,000
♫ Falling flower petals and flying catkins with the jackdaw ♫

86
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:30,460
♫ Songs needing a stringed accompaniment
perfectly encounter the pipa ♫

87
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:37,430
♫ Deep blue waves carry good fortune to the sea of people ♫

88
00:08:37,430 --> 00:08:41,050
♫ Youths grasp for dreams high among the clouds ♫

89
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:43,260
Like I said, none of you could beat me!

90
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:44,560
I admire you, Brother Rong!

91
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,190
What are you looking at?

92
00:08:46,190 --> 00:08:48,620
I want to treat you to a meal.

93
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:55,790
Rivers run in the tall mountains.

94
00:08:56,810 --> 00:08:58,690
A soulmate is hard to find.

95
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:03,210
I, Cao Weining, will never

96
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,510
fail A'Xiang for even a moment!

97
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:12,410
♫ Wind scoops sand as the years pass and grasps the reins
of mountain and rivers to walk the world ♫

98
00:09:12,410 --> 00:09:19,290
♫ Live a carefree life, without fears and without others ♫

99
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:22,480
♫ Side by side on a high tower, we pluck moonlight ♫

100
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:26,560
♫ and shine upon the city below ♫

101
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:33,170
♫ Passing years are melodious whispers, like the Qin sound ♫

102
00:09:33,930 --> 00:09:37,620
I have done nothing against my conscience my whole life!

103
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:39,790
Believe me, if you will, and if you don't,

104
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:42,010
further words are pointless!

105
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,280
Uncle Gao!

106
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:48,130
Uncle Gao!

107
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:58,340
♫ Youths grasp for dreams high up in clouds and pass by cliffs ♫

108
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,410
Wen Kexing...

109
00:10:03,170 --> 00:10:04,940
Was this the result you wanted?

110
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:10,200
Time slips away.

111
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:16,980
We promised to live and die together... yet I resent that we met too late.

112
